metadata.name: "Harlequin in The Land of Giants" - C Version
metadata.description:
Cesare Catania is an Italian artist, painter and sculptor. He began his successful career at a highly opportune time. In his art, tradition and innovation merge one another.

[Discover his Fantastic World HERE](https://linktr.ee/art_cesarecatania)


Title of Artwork:
Harlequin in the Land of Giants - C Version
Edition 1/1
Year: 2021
Technique: Digital Art

Variant of the oil on canvas A version, this surrealistic C Version is created exclusively for Digital World. Collect a unique piece of digital contemporary art!

A work of art full of meanings and metaphors about the World around us and more generally about the human condition. 

Harlequin (the human), the Giant (Companies and Multinationals), the Dice (the Giants play with us....), the Bishop (the strategy of Multinationals)  and all the secret details about this unique piece of art [HERE](https://www.cesarecatania.eu/en/portfolio/harlequin-in-the-land-of-giants-b-version-digital-art-and-nft/)

#contemporaryart #digitalart #nft
